31:21.613 --> 31:24.316
(groaning softly)

31:30.389 --> 31:31.623
(grunts)

31:33.225 --> 31:35.194
(panting)

31:35.227 --> 31:37.229
(sighs) Oh, man.

31:40.266 --> 31:42.268
(sighs)

31:49.241 --> 31:52.311
*

31:55.614 --> 31:56.815
It's not gonna kill you.

31:56.848 --> 31:58.317
Worked real hard for it.

31:58.350 --> 31:59.718
Would you look at this?

31:59.751 --> 32:02.588
If this isn't the saddest sight
I've ever seen.

32:02.621 --> 32:05.557
Oh, and I'm not just talking
about your face, Yoko.

32:05.591 --> 32:07.059
Hello, Cookie.

32:07.093 --> 32:08.927
It is never a pleasure
to see you.

32:11.097 --> 32:13.065
Congratulations,
little brother.

32:13.099 --> 32:15.067
Finally got your
throne, huh?

32:15.101 --> 32:16.468
Mm-hmm.

32:16.502 --> 32:18.170
Just be careful
up there.

32:18.204 --> 32:19.671
Brings out the darkness in you.

32:19.705 --> 32:20.506
Like you?

32:20.539 --> 32:22.241
Mm-hmm.
I ain't scared.

32:22.274 --> 32:23.742
But you should be.

32:23.775 --> 32:25.677
Of what I'm-a do
to your next album.

32:25.711 --> 32:27.113
You do know

32:27.146 --> 32:28.780
I can release it
whenever I want, right?

32:28.814 --> 32:30.316
COOKIE:
And that's exactly

32:30.349 --> 32:32.418
what we came here to
talk to you about, babe.

32:32.451 --> 32:33.819
Yeah?
Yeah.

32:33.852 --> 32:35.421
JAMAL: You see,
my Black and Whit album

32:35.454 --> 32:37.256
was a joint venture between
Empire and Lyon Dynasty,

32:37.289 --> 32:39.691
so I figure why not just
let Dynasty release it?

32:39.725 --> 32:42.361
You can't do that.
We own that album. Right, babe?

32:42.394 --> 32:44.663
Yeah.
Actually, they can,
baby brother.

32:44.696 --> 32:46.865
You see, there were never
any stipulations

32:46.898 --> 32:48.500
as to which label
would release it.

32:48.534 --> 32:51.170
Try it and I'll have you
tied up in court for years.

32:51.203 --> 32:53.805
Try it and we'll leak it online.
(chuckles)

32:53.839 --> 32:57.443
See, I learned a few things
from little King Hakeem, too.

32:57.476 --> 33:00.279
COOKIE: See, Hakeem,
we know this puts you in a jam.

33:00.312 --> 33:02.181
This could be terrible press
for you.

33:02.214 --> 33:04.983
Your first act as CEO,
the first thing you do

33:05.017 --> 33:06.152
is lose
your biggest artist?

33:06.185 --> 33:07.386
ANDRE:
Stock price will take a dive,

33:07.419 --> 33:09.188
but it should recover
in a year or two.

33:09.221 --> 33:11.657
Why are you doing this?

33:11.690 --> 33:13.292
You bring Lyon
Dynasty here, Ma.

33:13.325 --> 33:14.960
That would be a disaster.

33:14.993 --> 33:17.696
As much as I hate to agree
with her, Yo-ho is right.

33:17.729 --> 33:20.532
It would never work,
us together in the same company.

33:20.566 --> 33:23.502
Not unless I had full autonomy.

33:23.535 --> 33:25.137
And that's ridiculous.
ANDRE: Actually, it's not.

33:25.171 --> 33:27.739
Roc-A-Fella had the same deal
with Def Jam.

33:27.773 --> 33:29.308
Straight-up marketing
and distribution

33:29.341 --> 33:31.377
with no interference.

33:31.410 --> 33:34.080
Cookie has her own company under
Empire with no questions asked.

33:35.581 --> 33:37.583
Okay, I'm cool with that.
COOKIE: Okay.

33:37.616 --> 33:40.219
Well, then I want to be head
of A&R for all of Empire.

33:40.252 --> 33:41.687
ANDRE:
What are you doing?

33:41.720 --> 33:43.222
COOKIE: I'm negotiating.
I always wanted this.

33:43.255 --> 33:44.756
And I'd be damn good at it, too.

33:44.790 --> 33:46.158
I got the best ear
in the business.

33:46.192 --> 33:47.426
You all know it's true.

33:47.459 --> 33:49.861
Hakeem, don't do this.
Don't do it.

33:49.895 --> 33:51.897
You're gonna lose the company.

33:51.930 --> 33:53.599
They're gonna come in
and they're gonna dethrone you

33:53.632 --> 33:54.700
on the very first day.

33:54.733 --> 33:56.202
Everything you
worked for

33:56.235 --> 33:59.271
is gonna be gone,
just like that.

33:59.305 --> 34:01.740
Biggest mistake
you could make.

34:01.773 --> 34:04.176
Maybe.

34:04.210 --> 34:07.113
But I took my dad out
because he lost his way.

34:07.146 --> 34:09.047
But I did it
for all of us.

34:09.081 --> 34:11.683
So let's just come back
to Empire

34:11.717 --> 34:15.421
and let's be a real family
again, like we was before.

34:17.723 --> 34:20.292
Ma, you got yourself a deal.

34:31.737 --> 34:36.208
Well, you can use this place
for as long as you like.

34:36.242 --> 34:40.246
I know it's not Empire,
but it's got soul.

34:40.279 --> 34:42.414
Yeah, I kind of like
this vibe.

34:42.448 --> 34:45.050
Look, I need you to just
focus on music right now.

34:45.083 --> 34:46.385
Let me deal
with Camilla.

34:46.418 --> 34:48.654
No, I can help with her.
No.

34:48.687 --> 34:50.989
You sit your ass down
somewhere and write a song,

34:51.022 --> 34:53.392
and you leave the
dirty work to Cookie.

34:53.425 --> 34:56.162
Yes, ma'am. You the boss.
Yes.

34:56.195 --> 34:58.197
Mm. And don't you
ever forget that.

34:59.298 --> 35:01.133
(chuckles)

35:01.167 --> 35:02.934
You like it, don't you?
(laughs)

35:07.839 --> 35:09.841
(birds chirping)

35:23.489 --> 35:25.491
(exhales)

35:47.513 --> 35:49.515
(whispers):
I'm sorry.

35:58.156 --> 36:00.158
(whispers):
I'm sorry.

36:06.698 --> 36:08.567
(crying softly)

36:14.072 --> 36:17.476
God, help me.

36:17.509 --> 36:20.479
Please! (sobbing)

36:20.512 --> 36:23.515
* You can try
and take away my crown *

36:23.549 --> 36:26.685
* But I will never let
my kingdom down *

36:26.718 --> 36:30.489
* When I put it on,
it's on for real *

36:30.522 --> 36:33.425
* Damn, I wear it so well

36:33.459 --> 36:36.562
* I know that they comin'
for my throne *

36:36.595 --> 36:39.565
* But I'm the one
who got here on my own *

36:39.598 --> 36:43.201
* When I put it on,
it's on for real *

36:43.235 --> 36:45.237
* Damn, I wear it so well

36:45.271 --> 36:49.675
* I can still feel your eyes

36:49.708 --> 36:52.177
* On me like a spotlight

36:52.210 --> 36:56.081
* You held me up, up so high

36:56.114 --> 36:58.550
* So tell me, was it all lies?

36:58.584 --> 37:02.087
* Everything that I've done

37:02.120 --> 37:05.357
* Has got me
where I want to be *

37:05.391 --> 37:08.360
* So, baby,
why'd you have to leave? *

37:08.394 --> 37:11.363
* Whoa, oh...

37:11.397 --> 37:14.366
* When you got the world
in your hands *

37:14.400 --> 37:17.303
* Seems like everyone wants you
to fail *

37:17.336 --> 37:20.406
* It's like I've got a target
on my back *

37:20.439 --> 37:23.709
* Take a shot at me,
take a shot for me *

37:23.742 --> 37:26.712
* You can try
and take away my crown *

37:26.745 --> 37:30.081
* But I will never let
my kingdom down *

37:30.115 --> 37:33.619
* When I put it on,
it's on for real *

37:33.652 --> 37:35.721
* Damn, I wear it so well

37:35.754 --> 37:39.090
* I know that they comin'
for my throne *

37:39.124 --> 37:40.959
* But I'm the one
who got here... *

37:40.992 --> 37:42.428
What are you
doing here?

37:42.461 --> 37:44.396
I knocked,
and nobody was home.

37:44.430 --> 37:46.832
Everyone's at my grandma's
house. What do you want?

37:46.865 --> 37:49.335
Babe, I'm really sorry
on what I did.

37:49.368 --> 37:51.503
I know I was being an ass.

37:51.537 --> 37:53.339
I know.

37:53.372 --> 37:55.507
But you got to understand,
I broke up with you

37:55.541 --> 37:57.242
to get my empire back.

37:57.275 --> 38:00.011
But now that I got what's mine,
all I want is you.

38:00.045 --> 38:02.614
I don't understand.

38:02.648 --> 38:05.317
* Everyone wants a piece

38:05.351 --> 38:07.653
* Just so they can judge me

38:07.686 --> 38:11.289
* I thought I had your heart,
but you let me down *

38:11.323 --> 38:13.425
* And left me standing
all alone... *

38:13.459 --> 38:16.261
You sure you
want to do this?

38:16.294 --> 38:19.765
You promise me
we'll really be together?

38:19.798 --> 38:21.700
I promise.

38:21.733 --> 38:23.769
* When you got the world
in your hands *

38:23.802 --> 38:26.772
* Seems like everyone wants you
to fail *

38:26.805 --> 38:30.041
* It's like I've got a target
on my back *

38:30.075 --> 38:32.811
* Take a shot at me,
take a shot for me *

38:32.844 --> 38:36.448
* You can try
and take away my crown *

38:36.482 --> 38:39.785
* But I will never let
my kingdom down *

38:39.818 --> 38:42.988
* When I put it on,
it's on for real *

38:43.021 --> 38:44.990
* Damn, I wear it so well

38:45.023 --> 38:47.325
* I know that they comin'
for my throne... *

38:47.359 --> 38:48.960
I don't think
we should do this.

38:48.994 --> 38:50.796
Yes, Hakeem. Please.

38:50.829 --> 38:52.364
* On my own

38:52.398 --> 38:55.834
* When I put it on,
it's on for real *

38:55.867 --> 38:58.470
* Damn, I wear it so well

38:58.504 --> 39:01.407
* Oh, whoa...

39:01.440 --> 39:02.574
* Oh...

39:02.608 --> 39:04.843
Don't stop.

39:04.876 --> 39:07.513
* Oh, whoa...

39:07.546 --> 39:10.248
I love you.

39:11.282 --> 39:13.184
I love you, too.

39:14.586 --> 39:16.888
* Oh, whoa

39:16.922 --> 39:20.892
* Oh, whoa...

39:20.926 --> 39:24.062
* Damn, I wear it so well.

39:24.095 --> 39:26.097
(whistling tune)

39:36.307 --> 39:38.309
What's up?

39:40.145 --> 39:42.047
Come on over here.

39:42.080 --> 39:44.382
(train horn blowing
in distance)

39:51.156 --> 39:52.724
You have any idea

39:52.758 --> 39:54.793
where you're standing?

39:54.826 --> 39:56.995
Where?

39:58.997 --> 40:03.334
That's the spot where my
very best friend lost his life.

40:05.604 --> 40:07.973
He actually introduced me
to your mama.

40:08.006 --> 40:11.543
He damn near raised y'all
when I was on the road.

40:11.577 --> 40:14.880
He risked his life for me
on more than one occasion,

40:14.913 --> 40:17.583
and I risked mine for him.

40:17.616 --> 40:20.285
Except one night.

40:20.318 --> 40:22.454
And I shot him in the face.

40:24.923 --> 40:27.926
You know who I'm talking about.
It was your Uncle Bunkie.

40:30.762 --> 40:35.834
You see, that's how much
the empire means to me.

40:35.867 --> 40:39.237
And if you think you're gonna be
the CEO of my company,

40:39.270 --> 40:44.209
I will stop at nothing
to take it back.

40:46.277 --> 40:49.314
Since you're my baby boy,

40:49.347 --> 40:52.884
I got something for you.

40:54.953 --> 40:57.623
Take it.
Don't be scared.

40:57.656 --> 41:01.927
See, now's the time
for you to decide

41:01.960 --> 41:07.298
how far you're willing to go
to have the empire.

41:07.332 --> 41:10.802
You want to be king...

41:10.836 --> 41:13.505
kill your father
and sit on his throne.

41:13.539 --> 41:15.641
It's life or death.

41:15.674 --> 41:19.511
So if you don't shoot me
right here, I promise you,

41:19.545 --> 41:20.979
the next time I see you,

41:21.012 --> 41:24.315
I will do my best
to take your life.

41:24.349 --> 41:27.352
So shoot me,
so I don't have to do it to you.

41:33.925 --> 41:36.962
There you go.

41:36.995 --> 41:40.365
I know it's hard.

41:40.398 --> 41:42.834
But do it.

41:42.868 --> 41:44.402
It's okay.

41:46.437 --> 41:48.273
I'll make it easy
for you.

41:50.341 --> 41:52.678
You like stabbing people
in the back.

41:52.711 --> 41:55.881
Shoot me in the back.

41:55.914 --> 41:58.917
Oh, that's my boy.
I knew you could do it.

41:58.950 --> 42:00.919
Now pull the damn trigger.

42:00.952 --> 42:02.387
This what you want?

42:02.420 --> 42:04.222
Pull the damn trigger.

42:04.255 --> 42:06.257
(train clacking)

42:17.035 --> 42:19.905
I ain't got to do
what you want.

42:19.938 --> 42:21.139
(gun clatters on ground)

42:23.241 --> 42:25.343
Watch your back,

42:25.376 --> 42:27.779
baby boy!

42:27.813 --> 42:29.781
I keep my promises!

43:09.621 --> 43:10.722
Yeah.

